tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE LogicalRepresentations (Id INT PRIMARY KEY,
ProgramId INT,
Representation TEXT,
FOREIGN KEY(ProgramId) REFERENCES QuantumPrograms(Id));

CREATE TABLE qubit_connections (
    connection_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    qubit_source INTEGER NOT NULL,
    qubit_target INTEGER NOT NULL,
    connection_strength INTEGER,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
